title: Pogórze Przemyskie Landscape Park
text:
Pogórze Przemyskie Landscape Park ("Park Krajobrazowy Pogórze Przemyskie") is a <a href="protected%20area">protected area</a> (<a href="Landscape%20Park%20%28Poland%29">Landscape Park</a>) in south-eastern <a href="Poland">Poland</a>.
Geography.
The park protects an area of . It was established in 1991, and is a <a href="Natura%202000">Natura 2000</a> EU <a href="Special%20Protection%20Area">Special Protection Area</a>.
The Park lies within <a href="Podkarpackie%20Voivodeship">Podkarpackie Voivodeship</a>: 
Within the Landscape Park are nine <a href="nature%20reserve">nature reserve</a>s.
